                <p>Ourlex is web based URL tool. Grayscale is a free Bootstrap 3 theme created by Start Bootstrap. It can be yours right now, simply download the template on <a href="http://startbootstrap.com/template-overviews/grayscale/">the preview page</a>. The theme is open source, and you can use it for any purpose, personal or commercial.</p>
                <p>This theme features stock photos by <a href="http://gratisography.com/">Gratisography</a> along with a custom Google Maps skin courtesy of <a href="http://snazzymaps.com/">Snazzy Maps</a>.</p>
                <p>Grayscale includes full HTML, CSS, and custom JavaScript files along with LESS files for easy customization.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    
    
